{"tid":2001262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警以有共同目的為由驅散，唔比還押手足家屬送車。","createTime":"2020-05-04T11:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T13:51:17.000Z","uid":62369,"like":15,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"a6385bd9a3830c8e1c73c12aac1aea5e1e6d0714","tid":2001262,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:49:04.000Z","msg":"（獨媒特約報導）屯門裁判法院今日下午有涉反送中運動的案件上庭，多人前來聲援。惟在等候送車途中，突有至少6架警車抵達現場，數十名警員下車並以「限聚令」為名驅散聲援者，又拉起封鎖線及搜查年輕人，惡言斥：「你哋喺度有乜意思？」有目擊者稱，有還柙人士家屬欲送車也被趕離場，「喊到死」。<br />\n<br />\n今日第一次來旁聽的梁小姐，憶述下午約3時半與其他聲援人士於法院出口等候送囚車時，已有警車到達。及後接近4時半，數架警車相繼抵達，<span style=\"color: gold;\">隨即有數十名警員落地，驅散在場人士，指他們有「共同目的」，又高聲呼喝：「只有一次機會，你哋散唔散？」並即場於囚車出口拉起封鎖線，又搜查在場的年輕人。她指，警員至少在法院的三面駐守及驅散在場人士，也有便衣警與現場人士爭執。<br />\n梁小姐續稱，有還柙者母親欲送兒子車也「畀封鎖線推出嚟，喊到死」，直斥「好離譜，就算唔畀我哋，都應該畀人哋屋企人，見到佢阿媽真係好難過！」</span>說罷更激動落淚。她也因為被警員驅散，未能如願聲援還柙人士，「唔知（囚車）走咗未」。<br />\n屯門區議員曾錦榮及張可森等亦有到場監察。張可森斥，警方以限聚令為名驅散市民，甚至有旗手到場，阻礙親友送車：「就嚟母親節，母子見面都唔畀！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073083&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=6809f04d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073083&h=fd3ed795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073083</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">睇完好嬲，但係除咗好嬲我哋仲有好多野可以做。<br />\n雖然上Twitter 推文未必可以即時帶嚟啲咩大改變，但係Twitter 戰線係我哋connect 國際嘅好地方，香港人權民主法案通過到，Twitter 戰線功不可沒。<br />\n呢排Twitter 少咗人。<br />\n我哋唔知做咩可以成功，所以咩都試下，大家唔好放棄。<br />\n</span><br />\n呢條係關於呢件事嘅tweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tmclaughlin3/status/1257253345300934657?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftmclaughlin3%2Fstatus%2F1257253345300934657%3Fs%3D21&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=9db78364\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftmclaughlin3%2Fstatus%2F1257253345300934657%3Fs%3D21&h=e99e8c50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tmclaughlin3/status/1257253345300934657?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多其他關於香港抗爭同圍剿中共嘅國際報道<br />\n入去tg bot或者網站推晒佢哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Task 1 Task2 都要推呀</span><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 戰線手足整咗個網站出嚟比大家做task<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以後大家無藉口唔打國際線喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲bookmark 佢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/twitter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Ftwitter&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=736276b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/twitter</a><br />\n入bot 拎任務24小時更新：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1g5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=f0ea1061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>Like retweet reply</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n*如果見到想用嘅圖已經有手足用咗請搵第二張圖<br />\n*如果見到已經有好多圖就唔好再放圖，只留文字（短短地都得）<br />\n*唔好只係扔低張圖咩字都唔打<br />\n*唔知留咩好就like 手足留言或者啲對我哋有利嘅留言"},{"pid":"817900ff6631d8f7a25b03e4a79250d6800843ba","tid":2001262,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:49:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47be5f45717c6e237f736423d539634e46736ad1","tid":2001262,"uid":16676,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">廢除公安法</span></strong>先係基本<br />\n當年<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">臨立會</span></strong>拎返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a14cfb5c9ef7b5e371cbdfad8e48cd6023005f4","tid":2001262,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T11:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"